T1  - Quantifying location privacy in permissioned blockchain-based internet of things (IoT)
A1  - Shahid, Abdur R.
A1  - Pissinou, Niki
A1  - Njilla, Laurent
A1  - Alemany, Sheila
A1  - Imteaj, Ahmed
A1  - Makki, Kia
