T1  - A Comparative Study of Access Control Models for Ubiquitous Computing Systems
A1  - Renuse, Sayali
A1  - Mahalle, Parikshit N.
A1  - Shinde, Gitanjali Rahul
A1  - Sable, Nilesh P.
Y1  - 2023///
KW  - Access Control
KW  - IIoT
KW  - M2M Communication
