T1  - Blockchain-Based Zero-Knowledge Proofs for Data Privacy: Explore the Application of Blockchain Technology in facilitating Privacy-Preserving Transactions through Zero-Knowledge Proofs and Analyze their Effectiveness in Protecting Sensitive Data
A1  - Saroop, Shashank
