T1  - RouteNet-Fermi: Network Modeling With Graph Neural Networks
A1  - Ferriol-Galmes, Miquel
A1  - Paillisse, Jordi
A1  - Suarez-Varela, Jose
A1  - Rusek, Krzysztof
A1  - Xiao, Shihan
