T1  - NeuroCrypt: A Neuro Symbolic AI Ecosystem for Advanced Cryptographic Data Security and Transmission
A1  - Rajpal, Tanish Singh
A1  - Naithani, Akshit
Y1  - 2026///
KW  - Adaptive encryption
KW  - Shamir’s secret sharing
KW  - artificial intelligence
KW  - blockchain
KW  - neural cryptography
