T1  - DASHES—Autonomous and Secure Framework for Connected Healthcare With Consumer Electronics
A1  - Mahmood, Khalid
A1  - Alaidaros, Hashem
A1  - Ul Hassan, Mahmood
A1  - Huwaytim Alanazi, Meshari
A1  - Uddin, Mueen
