N2  - Migrant workers not only help fill the labor shortage, but they also make a substantial contribution to the economic growth. Existing research works on migrant workers assistance did not develop any mobile or web application with legal migration prediction, recruit agency, foreign mission, medical center search, emigration clearance, document attestation, remittance transfer, casting vote, and employment search features. In order to alleviate these issues, this article creates a smartphone application for migrant worker support that includes capabilities for detecting labor rights and legal migration, searching for recruit agencies, foreign missions, transferring remittances, and casting votes. This mobile application offers features for finding medical centers, finding a job, training, emigration clearance, document attestations, feedback on migration, and financial aid. Over 65 percent of the migrants provided very impactful comments regarding the planned application, according to the app's impact and potential analysis results.
