T1  - Screening Least Square Technique Assisted Multivariate Template Attack Against the Random Polynomial Generation of Dilithium
A1  - Fan, Haopeng
A1  - Zhang, Hailong
A1  - Wang, Yongjuan
A1  - Wang, Wenhao
A1  - Zhu, Yanbei
A1  - Zhang, Haojin
