N2  - With the advent of Internet & wireless network connectivity, the data usage has increased very rapidly in the past few years. Fourth-gen (4G) internet communication is still in scaling period but 5G is been rolled out in few countries. Now with almost 8-billion people on planet, AI, ML, and other technologies are in greater demand. The search for 6G has already began and is thought to be deployed worldwide soon. With more & more research in this area, the speed of internet is ultra-fast and with 6thGen it will be even faster. The 6G will revolutionize the IT & Technology industry in less than a decade from now. Nevertheless, there are some underlying challenges that occur with more speed and need to be resolved before providing it to masses. The issues are higher losses for small distance, lower latency, more system capacity etc. This paper helps in understanding the goal of 6thGen wireless network communication in future and its network's structure. Below we have described those new budding technologies like artificial intelligence, virtual reality, automated cars, block chain, three-dimensional networking, quantum communication, cloud computing, information transfer, remote access and analyzing big data that will help the 6G internet communication architecture development with the guaranteed transfer-rate we aim to achieve. All other technologies are also heighted alongside the expected applications of 6th Gen network communication. We have highlighted the hidden agendas and research related problems for attaining this target.
