N2  - Technology-rich environments still pose ever-present vulnerabilities, which necessitate the exploration of the integration of technological innovations and strategic frameworks with cybersecurity solutions and form the core discussion of this review paper. Based on this, it takes a holistic view of the landscape noting advances in artificial intelligence, machine learning, blockchain, and quantum, while highlighting policies, compliance, risk management, and multivocal strategies. Through interdependencies and synergies among innovations and frameworks, the paper concludes crucial performance indicators and comparative success metrics, leading toward a holistic approach to cybersecurity resilience. Such a synthesis offers significant insight into the potential future direction for academics and practitioners alike.
