T1  - Securing financial sector applications in the quantum era: a comprehensive evaluation of NIST's recommended algorithms through use-case analysis
A1  - Sadeghi, Somayeh
A1  - Chouhan, Vikas
A1  - Aldarwbi, Mohammed
A1  - Ghorbani, Ali
