T1  - SoCoMNNet: A SocioCognitive and memristive neural network-based context-aware GPS spoofing detection and mitigation in the Internet of drones
A1  - Nair, Aiswarya S.
A1  - Thampi, Sabu M.
A1  - P., Jithu Vijay V.
Y1  - 2025///
KW  - Context-aware intelligence
