T1  - A survey of cyber threat attribution: Challenges, techniques, and future directions
A1  - Prasad, Nilantha
A1  - Diro, Abebe
A1  - Warren, Matthew
A1  - Fernando, Mahesh
Y1  - 2025///
KW  - Artificial intelligence
KW  - Cyber security
