TY  - JOUR
T1  - Spatio-Temporal Multi-Metaverse Dynamic Streaming for Hybrid Quantum-Classical Systems
A1  - Park, Soohyun
A1  - Baek, Hankyul
A1  - Kim, Joongheon
Y1  - 2024/09//
KW  - Hybrid quantum-classical systems
