T1  - Trustworthy and Efficient Digital Twins in Post-Quantum Era with Hybrid Hardware-Assisted Signatures
A1  - Nouma, Saif E.
A1  - Yavuz, Attila A.
Y1  - 2024/03//
KW  - Additional Key Words and PhrasesMultimedia authent
KW  - cyber-security
