N2  - From the two-way perspective of technology and management, this paper discusses whether and how the file management department deal with the possible application tide of block chain. Firstly, the location, related technologies and applicable scenes of block chain technology in file management are re-recognized. Based on sorting out and identifying block chain systems, data and files, the file management (filing management and handover and reception) of files under the block chain technology environment is dialectically analyzed. Secondly, based on the case study at home and abroad, the paper concludes that "applying the existing blockchain technology framework"and "carrying out the research and development of file adaptability technology"are two ways for file and archive departments to actively apply blockchain. Finally, it is preliminarily judged that the application of blockchain technology by the file and archive management department will experience the development process of gradually accepting, deeply exploring, exerting influence and becoming an important member of the social governance system based on blockchain.
